

1. Produce qr-code:
    1.1 Code(API) to create qr-code.
    1.2 Info to encode (json) :
                           1.1 Name
                           1.2 Label
                           1.3 Inventory number

2. Read qr-code:
    3.1 Code(API) to decode qr picture
    3.2 Info from qr-code to client's screen

3. Turn on the camera -> Scan -> Analize -> Parse -> To the screen